Package: xrayvpn
Version: 0.1.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd
Maintainer: Gleb Ivanov <realglebivanov@gmail.com>
Description: Xray VPN with automatic route management
 xrayvpnd embeds xray-core with SOCKS inbound.
 tun2socksd creates a TUN device via tun2socks and forwards to xray.
 Fetches Russian IP ranges at startup, injects routing rules,
 manages fwmark-based split routing via netlink.
 Control: xrayvpn start|stop|status
